"Rumors regarding Vladimir Putin's absence have circulated, with unverified posts claiming he has not appeared in public for two to three weeks and appeared \"pale and unsteady\" during his last sighting. While the Kremlin denies these rumors, critics note a lack of press conferences for 10 days. Additionally, leaked documents allegedly suggest Putin secretly transferred power to Lavrov last month. However, one post includes a link claiming to show Putin, contradicting the disappearance narrative."